puthiya vaanam ( new sky ) is a 1988 tamil crime film directed by r. v. udayakumar . the film features sathyaraj , sivaji ganesan , rupini and gouthami in lead roles . the film , produced by g. thyagarajan and v. thamilazhagan , had musical score by hamsalekha and was released on 10 december 1988 . it was also 275th film of sivaji ganeshan . the film was named after a song from the film anbe vaa ( 1966 ) . the film was a remake of hindi film hukumat . sathyaraj character name in this film is mgrajarathnam by which he plays tribute to legendary mgr .